Data Visualization

#Pie Chart
table.iris = table(iris$Species)
pie(table.iris)

#Histogram
hist(iris$Sepal.Length)

#Box Plot
boxplot(Petal.Width ~ Species, data = iris)

#Scatter Plot
plot(x=iris$Petal.Length, y=iris$Petal.Width, col=iris$Species)

Machine Learning

#安裝rpart 套件
#install.packages('rpart')

#讀取rpart 套件
library(rpart)

#建立模型
fit <- rpart(Species ~ Sepal.Length + Sepal.Width + Petal.Length + Petal.Width,data= iris)

#繪製模型
plot(fit, margin = 0.2)
text(fit)

R Style

# prevent looping, using default function
s = 0 
for (i in seq(1,100)){
  s = s + i
}
s
## [1] 5050
sum(1:100)
## [1] 5050
# vectorized programming
b = c()
a = c(1,2,3,4,5)
for (i in a){
  b = c(b, i*i)
}
b
## [1]  1  4  9 16 25
a = c(1,2,3,4,5)
a = a ^ 2
a
## [1]  1  4  9 16 25
# preallocating
b = c()
a = c(1,2,3,4,5)
for (i in a){
  b = c(b, i*i)
}
b
## [1]  1  4  9 16 25
b = c(0,0,0,0,0)
a = c(1,2,3,4,6)
for (i in seq_along(a)){
  b[i] = a[i] ^ 2
}
b
## [1]  1  4  9 16 36
